458.jpeg\" alt=\" j\" width=\"620\" height=\"458\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>1986 Tour de Suisse</strong> Hinault leading at the Saint Gotthard Pass.</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Photograph: Gamma-Keystone via Getty Images</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"b5deb64fc16184aba95e02556fa3567a394f7d52\"> <img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/11/14/1415965009419/8d0ceda0-5f75-4da7-9fd7-f19ef2d4805a-620x411.jpeg\" alt=\"21 Jul 1986, Alpe-d'Huez, France Bernard Hinaultm right, and Greg Lemond, wearing the leader's yellow jersey, climb the Alpe d'Huez mountain pass during stage 18 of the 1986 Tour de France\" width=\"620\" height=\"411\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>July 1986, Alpe-d’Huez, France</strong> Hinault, right, and Lemond, wearing the leader’s yellow jersey, climb the mountain pass during stage 18 of the 1986 Tour de France.</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Photograph: Robert Pratt/Reuters/Corbis</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"94d6921440450d39bda277465ed1e20e9a0656f5\"> <img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/11/14/1415962011893/9f3235d9-4df7-4aba-a5c4-fcb9c8556096-620x413.jpeg\" alt=\"Bernard Hinault, right, and his teammate Greg Lemond smile as they cross the finish line together at the end of the 18th stage of the 1986 Tour de France\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>1986 Tour de France</strong> Hinault, right, and his team-mate Greg Lemond smile as they cross the finish line together at the end of the stage 18 between Briançon and Alpe d’Huez. Hinault won the stage and Lemond retained his leader’s yellow jersey and went on to win his first Tour, becoming the first America